{"tid":1952783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不費一兵一卒，又贏] 美國確診病例突破18萬　死亡人數多過中國","createTime":"2020-03-31T21:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T22:47:55.000Z","uid":269148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb01884753ee0c3268c4a301fc9e84ce324b9382","tid":1952783,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:10:23.000Z","msg":"美國確診病例突破18萬　死亡人數多過中國<br />\n<br />\n美國確診新型冠狀病毒的人數突破18萬，累計超過3600人死亡，超越中國，成為繼意大利和西班後，死亡人數第三多的國家。重災區紐約州佔的確診病例7萬5千多宗，其中接近4萬1千宗在紐約。紐約州州長葛謨說，要加倍努力才可以戰勝疫情。另外，葛謨任職電視新聞主播的弟弟克里斯亦確診。<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-01 05:03:55"},{"pid":"e4880a0601499aceb1fb5e7f2aa316a0615773ad","tid":1952783,"uid":24339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:11:42.000Z","msg":"支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3e0b5050a684ceef844ef0f19bbe5c8e039f4d","tid":1952783,"uid":208201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:19:00.000Z","msg":"美國最後會唔會過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a030cc5539da4634cd475c3e8fc72438992df52b","tid":1952783,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:25:49.000Z","msg":"之前又話美國軍人係運動會播毒既藍絲宜家去晒邊"},{"pid":"d765807466b26703f2fb852855aea18afd91da30","tid":1952783,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:58:32.000Z","msg":"日日都多咁多單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ce40f7a6a2382f6542099ba6837cee31ed5963","tid":1952783,"uid":119232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a030cc5539da4634cd475c3e8fc72438992df52b","tid":1952783,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T21:25:49.000Z","msg":"之前又話美國軍人係運動會播毒既藍絲宜家去晒邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T22:03:43.000Z","msg":"武漢根本派左好多人去播毒"},{"pid":"fdc0f9ebcbbfc3c4bda43ebe6d7b83d455f8c789","tid":1952